#. type: text
#: docs/zh/community/release_policy.md:0
msgid "# 版本发布策略"
msgstr "# Release Policy"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/community/release_policy.md:2
msgid "## 版本编号"
msgstr "## Version Numbering"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/community/release_policy.md:4
msgid "Triton-Ascend 遵循 [PEP 440](https://peps.python.org/pep-0440/) 版本规范，版本号与上游 Triton 对齐：`vMAJOR.MINOR.PATCH[rcN][.postN]`"
msgstr "Triton-Ascend follows the [PEP 440](https://peps.python.org/pep-0440/) version specification, with version numbers aligned with upstream Triton: `vMAJOR.MINOR.PATCH[rcN][.postN]`"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/community/release_policy.md:6
msgid ""
"- **MAJOR.MINOR**：与上游 Triton 版本一一对应，例如 Triton-Ascend `3.2` 基于 Triton `3.2`\n"
"- **PATCH**：Triton-Ascend 的 `PATCH` 版本可能高于上游 Triton，用于 `MAJOR.MINOR` 级别的问题修复或改进，例如 Triton-Ascend `3.2.0` 和 `3.2.1` 均基于 Triton `3.2.0`\n"
"- **rcN**：发布候选版本，根据需要发布以供社区早期测试和反馈\n"
"- **postN**：已发布版本的后续补丁，根据需要发布以修复稳定版本中的问题\n"
msgstr ""
"- **MAJOR.MINOR**: Corresponds one-to-one with the upstream Triton version. For example, Triton-Ascend `3.2` is based on Triton `3.2`.\n"
"- **PATCH**: The `PATCH` version of Triton-Ascend may be higher than the upstream Triton, used for bug fixes or improvements at the `MAJOR.MINOR` level. For example, both Triton-Ascend `3.2.0` and `3.2.1` are based on Triton `3.2.0`.\n"
"- **rcN**: Release candidate version, released as needed for early community testing and feedback.\n"
"- **postN**: Subsequent patch for a released version, released as needed to fix issues in a stable version.\n"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/community/release_policy.md:8
msgid "## 分支策略"
msgstr "## Branch Strategy"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/community/release_policy.md:10
msgid ""
"- `main` 分支为最新开发分支，跟踪最新上游 Triton 版本\n"
"- 每个发布版本创建对应的发布开发分支（如 `release/3.2.x`），与社区发布具有相同的 commit id\n"
"- 功能开发应在 fork 仓库中进行，通过 `PR` 合入 Triton-Ascend 仓库\n"
msgstr ""
"- The `main` branch is the latest development branch, tracking the latest upstream Triton version.\n"
"- Each release version creates a corresponding release development branch (e.g., `release/3.2.x`), which has the same commit ID as the community release.\n"
"- Feature development should be carried out in a forked repository and merged into the Triton-Ascend repository via a `PR`.\n"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/community/release_policy.md:12
msgid "**`main` 分支映射：**"
msgstr "**`main` branch mapping:**"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/community/release_policy.md:14
msgid ""
"| Triton-Ascend | Triton commit hash                                           | Python    | CANN  | PyTorch | LLVM commit hash                                             | 补丁                                                        |\n"
"| ------------- | ------------------------------------------------------------ | --------- | ----- | ------- | ------------------------------------------------------------ | ------------------------------------------------------------ |\n"
"| `main`        | [cfc0a9d](https://github.com/triton-lang/triton-ascend/commit/cfc0a9d) | `3.9~3.13` | `9.0.0` | `2.7.1`   | [fad3272](https://github.com/llvm/llvm-project/commit/fad3272) | [fad3272.patch](https://github.com/triton-lang/triton-ascend/blob/main/third_party/ascend/llvm_patch/fad3272.patch) |\n"
msgstr ""
"| Triton-Ascend | Triton commit hash                                           | Python    | CANN  | PyTorch | LLVM commit hash                                             | Patch                                                        |\n"
"| ------------- | ------------------------------------------------------------ | --------- | ----- | ------- | ------------------------------------------------------------ | ------------------------------------------------------------ |\n"
"| `main`        | [cfc0a9d](https://github.com/triton-lang/triton-ascend/commit/cfc0a9d) | `3.9~3.13` | `9.0.0` | `2.7.1`   | [fad3272](https://github.com/llvm/llvm-project/commit/fad3272) | [fad3272.patch](https://github.com/triton-lang/triton-ascend/blob/main/third_party/ascend/llvm_patch/fad3272.patch) |\n"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/community/release_policy.md:16
msgid "## 维护分支与生命周期"
msgstr "## Maintenance Branches and Lifecycle"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/community/release_policy.md:18
msgid "维护分支状态包括："
msgstr "Maintenance branch status includes:"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/community/release_policy.md:20
msgid ""
"- **活跃（Active）**：持续接受缺陷修复、功能改进和安全补丁；将继续演进功能或发布新版本\n"
"- **维护（Maintenance）**：仅接受关键缺陷修复和安全补丁；不再发布功能改进\n"
"- **停止维护（End of Life）**：不再接受任何修复；分支维护已停止\n"
msgstr ""
"- **Active**: Continuously receives bug fixes, feature enhancements, and security patches; will continue to evolve features or release new versions  \n"
"- **Maintenance**: Only accepts critical bug fixes and security patches; no longer releases feature enhancements  \n"
"- **End of Life**: No longer accepts any fixes; branch maintenance has ceased\n"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/community/release_policy.md:22
msgid ""
"| 分支              | 状态     | Triton 版本 | Triton-Ascend 发布              | 维护截止 |\n"
"| ----------------- | -------- | ------------ | ----------------------------------- | -------- |\n"
"| `main`            | `活跃`   | `3.5.0`      | /                                   | /        |\n"
"| `release/3.2.1` | `活跃`   | `3.2.0`      | `3.2.1`                             | /        |\n"
"| `release/3.2.x` | `维护`   | `3.2.0`      | `3.2.0rc2`，`3.2.0rc3`，`3.2.0rc4`，`3.2.0` | /        |\n"
msgstr ""
"| Branch             | Status   | Triton Version | Triton-Ascend Release              | Maintenance End |\n"
"| ----------------- | -------- | -------------- | ----------------------------------- | -------------- |\n"
"| `main`            | `Active` | `3.5.0`        | /                                   | /              |\n"
"| `release/3.2.1`   | `Active` | `3.2.0`        | `3.2.1`                             | /              |\n"
"| `release/3.2.x`   | `Maintenance` | `3.2.0`    | `3.2.0rc2`, `3.2.0rc3`, `3.2.0rc4`, `3.2.0` | /              |\n"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/community/release_policy.md:24
msgid "## 发布周期"
msgstr "## Release Cycle"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/community/release_policy.md:26
msgid ""
"- **稳定版本**：按照项目版本节奏发布，并非每个上游 Triton 版本都会有对应的稳定发布\n"
"- **rc 版本**：与上游 Triton 版本节奏同步发布，供用户早期测试\n"
"- **post 版本**：根据需要发布，用于修复现有稳定版本中的问题\n"
msgstr ""
"- **Stable version**: Released according to the project version cadence; not every upstream Triton version will have a corresponding stable release.\n"
"- **rc version**: Released in sync with the upstream Triton version cadence for early user testing.\n"
"- **post version**: Released as needed to fix issues in existing stable versions.\n"

